{"article_id":"P55N5EMTIJMY3Pc6","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"WASHINGTON/NEW YORK","depth":1},{"id":1,"text":"( ) -","depth":2},{"id":2,"text":"President Donald Trump on Wednesday said","depth":9},{"id":3,"text":"he could withdraw his support for Brett Kavanaugh","depth":10},{"id":4,"text":"depending on the testimony in a high-profile Thursday hearing into multiple accusations of sexual misconduct against the Supreme Court nominee .","depth":10},{"id":5,"text":"Trump defended Kavanaugh , now a federal appeals court judge , at a New York news conference ,","depth":10},{"id":6,"text":"but the president ' s comments injected another note of uncertainty into Kavanaugh ' s already troubled bid for a lifetime appointment to the nation ' s highest court .","depth":10},{"id":7,"text":"\" You know ,","depth":12},{"id":8,"text":"believe it or not ,","depth":12},{"id":9,"text":"I ' m going to see what ' s said \" at the hearing ,","depth":11},{"id":10,"text":"Trump told reporters .","depth":10},{"id":11,"text":"A third woman has accused Kavanaugh of aggressive sexual behavior in the 1980s .","depth":8},{"id":12,"text":"The nominee has vehemently denied all of the allegations ahead of the Senate Judiciary Committee hearing","depth":9},{"id":13,"text":"coming up on Thursday","depth":10},{"id":14,"text":"where one of his accusers , Christine Blasey Ford , will also testify to senators .","depth":10},{"id":15,"text":"Trump dismissed the allegations against Kavanaugh as a \" big fat con job \"","depth":8},{"id":16,"text":"orchestrated by Democrats .","depth":8},{"id":17,"text":"He did not say","depth":10},{"id":18,"text":"that Kavanaugh ' s female accusers were lying .","depth":10},{"id":19,"text":"\" I can always be convinced , \"","depth":10},{"id":20,"text":"Trump said .","depth":10},{"id":21,"text":"\" It will be interesting to hear what she has to say . \"","depth":8},{"id":22,"text":"Trump himself has faced multiple accusations of sexual misconduct .","depth":9},{"id":23,"text":"He said","depth":10},{"id":24,"text":"this has shaped his view of the allegations against Kavanaugh .","depth":10},{"id":25,"text":"\" I ' ve had a lot of false charges made against me , \"","depth":10},{"id":26,"text":"he said .","depth":10},{"id":27,"text":"\" When I see it ,","depth":10},{"id":28,"text":"I view it differently than someone","depth":11},{"id":29,"text":"sitting home","depth":13},{"id":30,"text":"watching television","depth":13},{"id":31,"text":"where they say ,","depth":13},{"id":32,"text":"' Oh , Judge Kavanaugh this and that . ' \"","depth":13},{"id":33,"text":"Blasey Ford will tell the committee","depth":10},{"id":34,"text":"a \" visibly drunk \" Kavanaugh and a friend locked her in a bedroom at a party in a Washington suburb in 1982 ,","depth":11},{"id":35,"text":"when she was 15","depth":12},{"id":36,"text":"and he was 17 ,","depth":12},{"id":37,"text":"according to testimony","depth":10},{"id":38,"text":"released ahead of the hearing .","depth":10},{"id":39,"text":"Blasey Ford says","depth":10},{"id":40,"text":"Kavanaugh climbed on top of her ,","depth":11},{"id":41,"text":"tried to take off her clothes ,","depth":12},{"id":42,"text":"and put his hand over her mouth","depth":13},{"id":43,"text":"when she tried to scream for help .","depth":13},{"id":44,"text":"\" It was hard for me to breathe ,","depth":11},{"id":45,"text":"and I thought","depth":12},{"id":46,"text":"Brett was accidentally going to kill me , \"","depth":12},{"id":47,"text":"her testimony says .","depth":10},{"id":48,"text":"Kavanaugh will deny all of the allegations","depth":7},{"id":49,"text":"but will tell the committee","depth":9},{"id":50,"text":"that he was \" not perfect \" in high school .","depth":9},{"id":51,"text":"\" I drank beer with my friends , usually on weekends .","depth":10},{"id":52,"text":"Sometimes I had too many .","depth":10},{"id":53,"text":"In retrospect , I said and did things in high school","depth":11},{"id":54,"text":"that make me cringe now , \"","depth":11},{"id":55,"text":"he said in testimony","depth":11},{"id":56,"text":"released on Wednesday .","depth":11},{"id":57,"text":"Republican Judiciary committee staffers on Wednesday were trying to interview another woman , Julie Swetnick .","depth":5},{"id":58,"text":"Earlier in the day , she said","depth":9},{"id":59,"text":"she attended more than 10 house parties in the Washington area from 1981 to 1983","depth":10},{"id":60,"text":"where Kavanaugh was present .","depth":10},{"id":61,"text":"She described gang rapes","depth":11},{"id":62,"text":"she said","depth":13},{"id":63,"text":"occurred","depth":13},{"id":64,"text":"in which boys would line up","depth":13},{"id":65,"text":"to rape incapacitated girls .","depth":13},{"id":66,"text":"\" In approximately 1982 , I became the victim of one of these ' gang ' or ' train ' rapes","depth":15},{"id":67,"text":"where Mark Judge and Brett Kavanaugh were present , \"","depth":15},{"id":68,"text":"she said ,","depth":15},{"id":69,"text":"mentioning the name of a close friend of Kavanaugh .","depth":15},{"id":70,"text":"She did not identify her attackers","depth":14},{"id":71,"text":"and did not accuse Kavanaugh of taking part .","depth":14},{"id":72,"text":"\" During the incident , I was incapacitated","depth":15},{"id":73,"text":"without my consent","depth":15},{"id":74,"text":"and unable to fight off the boys","depth":15},{"id":75,"text":"raping me .","depth":15},{"id":76,"text":"I believe","depth":15},{"id":77,"text":"I was drugged","depth":16},{"id":78,"text":"using Quaaludes","depth":18},{"id":79,"text":"( a sedative )","depth":18},{"id":80,"text":"or something similar","depth":18},{"id":81,"text":"placed in what I was drinking , \"","depth":18},{"id":82,"text":"she said .","depth":14},{"id":83,"text":"She also said","depth":13},{"id":84,"text":"she witnessed efforts by Kavanaugh and others","depth":15},{"id":85,"text":"\" to cause girls to become inebriated and disoriented","depth":16},{"id":86,"text":"so they could then be ' gang raped ' in a side room or a bedroom by a ' train ' of numerous boys , \"","depth":16},{"id":87,"text":"adding","depth":15},{"id":88,"text":"she remembers boys","depth":17},{"id":89,"text":"including Kavanaugh","depth":17},{"id":90,"text":"getting in lines","depth":17},{"id":91,"text":"to take part in these rapes .","depth":17},{"id":92,"text":"She did not identify the individuals","depth":13},{"id":93,"text":"directly involved in those assaults .","depth":13},{"id":94,"text":"Kavanaugh said in a statement","depth":12},{"id":95,"text":"released by the White House ,","depth":12},{"id":96,"text":"\" This is ridiculous and from the Twilight Zone .","depth":11},{"id":97,"text":"I don ' t know","depth":12},{"id":98,"text":"who this is","depth":12},{"id":99,"text":"and this never happened . \"","depth":11},{"id":100,"text":"Swetnick is represented by lawyer Michael Avenatti ,","depth":10},{"id":101,"text":"who also represents adult film star Stormy Daniels in a lawsuit against Trump","depth":11},{"id":102,"text":"to void a nondisclosure agreement","depth":12},{"id":103,"text":"under which the president ' s former personal lawyer paid her $ 130,000","depth":13},{"id":104,"text":"not to discuss her alleged relationship with Trump years ago .","depth":13},{"id":105,"text":"Swetnick and Avenatti did not immediately respond to requests for comment .","depth":9},{"id":106,"text":"On Twitter , Trump called Avenatti \" a total low-life \" and \" a third rate lawyer","depth":10},{"id":107,"text":"who is good at making false accusations . \"","depth":10},{"id":108,"text":"Avenatti responded on Twitter ,","depth":10},{"id":109,"text":"calling Trump \" a habitual liar and complete narcissist . \"","depth":10},{"id":110,"text":"In an interview with Fox News on Monday , Kavanaugh was asked","depth":9},{"id":111,"text":"whether he ever participated in or was aware of any gang rape at a party","depth":10},{"id":112,"text":"he attended .","depth":10},{"id":113,"text":"\" That ' s totally false and outrageous .","depth":10},{"id":114,"text":"I ' ve never done any such thing , \"","depth":10},{"id":115,"text":"he responded .","depth":9},{"id":116,"text":"Another woman , Deborah Ramirez , has accused Kavanaugh of exposing himself during a drunken dormitory party during the 1983-84 academic year","depth":10},{"id":117,"text":"when both attended Yale University .","depth":10},{"id":118,"text":"Kavanaugh has denied that allegation as well .","depth":9},{"id":119,"text":"Republican staffers on the committee also asked Kavanaugh about two other incidents","depth":11},{"id":120,"text":"involving alcohol and sexual behavior ,","depth":11},{"id":121,"text":"according to a transcript of an interview","depth":11},{"id":122,"text":"released on Wednesday .","depth":11},{"id":123,"text":"Kavanaugh told staffers","depth":10},{"id":124,"text":"they did not take place ,","depth":11},{"id":125,"text":"and nobody has come forward","depth":12},{"id":126,"text":"to speak publicly about them .","depth":12},{"id":127,"text":"Supreme Court appointments must be confirmed by the Senate .","depth":7},{"id":128,"text":"Trump ' s fellow Republicans control the chamber by a narrow 51-49 margin .","depth":8},{"id":129,"text":"So , Republican defections could sink the nomination .","depth":8},{"id":130,"text":"The fight over the Supreme Court has been unfolding just weeks ahead of the Nov. 6 congressional elections","depth":9},{"id":131,"text":"in which Democrats will seek to take majority control of the Senate and the House of Representatives from the Republicans .","depth":9},{"id":132,"text":"Trump chose Kavanaugh , a conservative appeals court judge , for the court in July , after the retirement of Justice Anthony Kennedy .","depth":9},{"id":133,"text":"If confirmed ,","depth":11},{"id":134,"text":"Kavanaugh would cement conservative control of the court ,","depth":11},{"id":135,"text":"as Trump moves to shift the high court and the broader federal judiciary to the right .","depth":10},{"id":136,"text":"A committee vote on the nomination was expected on Friday , with a final Senate vote on Tuesday .","depth":8},{"id":137,"text":"Republican Senator Chuck Grassley , the Judiciary Committee ' s chairman , said","depth":11},{"id":138,"text":"the hearing will go forward","depth":13},{"id":139,"text":"as planned","depth":13},{"id":140,"text":"and that the panel ' s staff is looking into Swetnick ' s allegations .","depth":12},{"id":141,"text":"Senate Democratic Leader Chuck Schumer and all the Judiciary Committee ' s Democrats called on Kavanaugh to withdraw in light of the allegations ,","depth":11},{"id":142,"text":"and said","depth":12},{"id":143,"text":"if he does not ,","depth":13},{"id":144,"text":"an FBI investigation is needed","depth":14},{"id":145,"text":"before any Senate confirmation vote .","depth":14},{"id":146,"text":"The pitched battle over Kavanaugh added to perceptions of Washington as paralyzed by partisan rancor .","depth":9},{"id":147,"text":"U.S. Supreme Court nominee Brett Kavanaugh departs his suburban Washington home in Chevy Chase , Maryland , U.S.","depth":6},{"id":148,"text":"September 26 , 2018 .","depth":7},{"id":149,"text":"/Al Drago","depth":7},{"id":150,"text":"Senator Jeff Flake , a moderate Republican , issued a plea for civility .","depth":5},{"id":151,"text":"\" We sometimes seem intent on stripping people of their humanity","depth":6},{"id":152,"text":"so that we might more easily disregard or defame them","depth":7},{"id":153,"text":"and put them through the grinder","depth":8},{"id":154,"text":"that our politics requires .","depth":8}],"relations":[{"parent":309,"left":0,"right":308,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":308,"left":1,"right":307,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":307,"left":279,"right":306,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":279,"left":209,"right":278,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":209,"left":1